snippet.title: WITNESS Statement of JOHNNY DEPP's Assistant! - STEPHEN DEUTERS
snippet.description:
The FULL witness statement of Stephen Deuters, Johnny Depp's former personal assistant from when Johnny Depp and Amber Heard were together. He tells the truth about what Amber Heard did to Johnny Depp.

This is one of multiple videos to be released, each covering another witness statement from the Johnny Depp v The Sun trial in the UK.

Big thanks to Les for doing the voice over for each female witness.
